<plot>Le Centre National d'Art et de Culture Georges Pompidou , better known as 'Centre Pompidou' or 'Beaubourg' celebrates its tenth birthday. Thirteen personalities are interviewed about this first decade (1977-1987) and their words are illustrated by archive images, a complete visit of the centre and an overview of the most important exhibitions that took place there.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?324305</url></doc>
